document_data.mainbody:
The '''''Rules Expansion Gift Set''''' is a boxed set containing three sourcebooks and one Dungeon Master's screen for 5{{th}}-edition ''[[Dungeons & Dragons]]''. Two of the sourcebooks are updated versions of older rule sourcebooks, namely ''[[Tasha's Cauldron of Everything]]'' and ''[[Xanathar's Guide to Everything]]''. The third, ''[[Mordenkainen Presents: Monsters of the Multiverse]]'', collects and revises hundreds of monster stat blocks and thirty player race options from several previously published sources.

{{Quote|'''Expanded Rules. Expanded Foes. Expanded Adventure!'''<br />
Embark on a journey with the rival wizards Tasha and Mordenkainen and the crime lord Xanathar. Learn new secrets and discover magical new ways to play the world's greatest roleplaying game.<br />
Crafted for DMs and players alike, this collection brings together all the fifth edition rules expansion books in one set, complete with a beautiful new Dungeon Master's screen.}}
{{-}}
